@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@
+The branch onair-build-version was created to have there the version that works better with our
+app, and build the release versions of it using it.
+
+This had to be done because of an error on the latest version of the facebook-android-sdk
+that makes the app crash when login with FB for the first time.
+(See https://github.com/OnAirPlayer/OnAirPlayer-Android/issues/71)
\ No newline at end of file
